  "subject": "Fix code quality issues in dmi-service",
  "commit_message": "Fix code quality issues in dmi-service\n\n  - Use Java 17 pattern matching for instanceof\n  - Make injected fields final with @RequiredArgsConstructor\n  - Remove unused fields and imports\n  - Fix naming conventions and typos\n  - Replace lambda with method reference where applicable\n  - Use == for enum comparison\n  - Extract magic strings to constants\n  - Update tests to use constructor injection\n\nIssue-ID: CPS-475\nChange-Id: I99141221a2705da6ef16161930adba7f3f488bed\nSigned-off-by: ToineSiebelink <toine.siebelink@est.tech>\n",
